data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER!!  
 Are you looking for your own slice of heaven? Close to the schools and a quick jog to town, enjoy peaceful, country living in this beautiful 4 bed 2.5bath home with a wood burning fireplace, a large master bedroom updated with beautiful rustic wood, 4th bedroom is a bonus room that is currently used as a bedroom, closet, and pantry but could easily be turned back to one large room if needed. Sits on 7.7 acres M/L with a 30 X 60 shop, a 38 X 60 barn with 9 stables, 2 runs, and a tack room, fully fenced and ready for animals, a newer 32ft round above ground pool with deck and a brand new Hayward pump, a storage building, and don't forget the storm shelter!  This place is set up for the perfect hobby farm or just plenty of room for your family to run!
